OL,3,CCardiff City to honour 'club legend'
OL,4,CSol Bamba at Derby County fixture
OL,6,FCardiff City will pay tributes to
OL,7,F"club legend" Sol Bamba ahead of their
OL,8,Ffixture against Derby County this
OL,9,Fweekend.
OL,11,FThe Bluebirds faithful will be able
OL,12,Fpay their respects to Bamba with a
OL,13,Fminute of applause ahead of kick-off
OL,14,Fat Pride Park.
OL,16,FThe defender died age 39 while working
OL,17,Fas a technical director at Turkish
OL,18,Fclub Adanaspor on August 31.
