OL,3,CCardiff City to honour 'club legend'
OL,4,CSol Bamba at Derby County fixture
OL,6,FSpeaking to the media this afternoon,
OL,7,FCardiff City manager Erol Bulut said:
OL,8,F"I know him as a player from
OL,9,FTrabzonspor so I met him also last
OL,10,Fseason when we started.
OL,12,F"Great guy, great character and I met
OL,13,Fhim a few times. We talk a little bit.
OL,14,FA really, really good person. As a
OL,15,Fplayer (he) was also a great one.
OL,17,F"Of course, for Cardiff City fans he's
OL,18,Fone of the best players. He was very
OL,19,Fgood with the fan base.
