OL,6,F"When I read about that, I got a
OL,7,Fshock. I thought something was wrong
OL,8,Fso I was calling a few friends I know
OL,9,Fin Turkey. He was 39 years old. It
OL,10,Fcomes too quick. It hurts. It hurts."
OL,12,FBamba made more than 100 appearances
OL,13,Ffor the Bluebirds across five years in
OL,14,FSouth Wales as a player and cemented
OL,15,Fhimself in Cardiff City history in
OL,16,F2018 as part of the side which won
OL,17,Fpromotion to the Premier League.
