OL,3,CCardiff City to honour 'club legend'
OL,4,CSol Bamba at Derby County fixture
OL,6,FIn a statement, the club said: "It is
OL,7,Fwith the deepest sadness that we have
OL,8,Flearnt this evening about the passing
OL,9,Fof Club legend, Sol Bamba.
OL,11,F"As a player and coach, Sol's impact
OL,12,Fon our football club was immeasurable.
OL,13,FHe was a hero to all of us, a leader
OL,14,Fin every dressing room and a true
OL,15,Fgentleman.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with his friends,
OL,18,Ffamily and everyone lucky enough to
OL,19,Fknow and love Sol."
