OL,6,FBamba was diagnosed with Non-Hodgkin
OL,7,Flymphoma in 2021 while at Cardiff, but
OL,8,Fwas declared cancer-free after a
OL,9,Fcourse of chemotherapy and returned to
OL,10,Fplay again for the Bluebirds.
OL,12,FA club statement said Bamba had fallen
OL,13,Fill before a match and was taken to
OL,14,Fhospital where he died.
OL,16,FHis wife, Chloe, wrote on Instagram:
OL,17,F"For the last few years I have watched
OL,18,FSol fight his cancer head on with an
OL,19,Fastounding mental and physical
OL,20,Fstrength.
