OL,3,CCardiff City to honour 'club legend'
OL,4,CSol Bamba at Derby County fixture
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, it was never a fair
OL,7,Ffight and just when things were
OL,8,Flooking up he took a downturn and
OL,9,Ffinally succumbed on 31st August.
OL,11,FShe said the past few years have been
OL,12,F"indescribably difficult" but the
OL,13,Fcouple "still managed to find joy and
OL,14,Flaughter."
OL,16,FShe continued: "It was an honour to
OL,17,Fhave loved and been loved by Sol. I
OL,18,Flearnt so much form him. He is my
OL,19,Fhero. My heart is breaking. What a
OL,20,Fgift, what a gift to have been loved
OL,21,Fby him."
