OL,6,FAfter leaving the Bluebirds to team up
OL,7,Fwith former boss Neil Warnock at
OL,8,Ffellow Championship outfit
OL,9,FMiddlesborough, Bamba returned to the
OL,10,FWelsh capital as part of Sambri
OL,11,FLamouchi's coaching staff.
OL,13,FTaking to X, formerly Twitter, Warnock
OL,14,Fsaid: "I can't believe I won't see
OL,15,Fthat beaming smile again. I'm so happy
OL,16,Fthat Sol was part of my life and we
OL,17,Fhad such brilliant memories together.
